China's four-time Olympian Qi Guangpu won his first gold medal in the freestyle skiing men's aerials final at the Beijing 2022 Winter Olympics on Wednesday. France's Clement Noel won the gold medal in the alpine skiing men's slalom at the Beijing 2022 Winter Olympics on Wednesday. Four years ago in PeyongChang, South Korea, he finished 4th, 0.04 seconds from a bronze medal.